-- Clermont Auvergne Routs Exeter 46-12 in Heineken Cup Rugby Match
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-10-20T19:20:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-20/clermont-auvergne-routs-exeter-46-12-in-heineken-cup-rugby-match.html
Clermont Auvergne routed Exeter
46-12 to move above defending champion Leinster in Pool 5 of
rugby’s Heineken Cup.  Wesley Fofana and Napolini Nalaga each touched down twice
as Clermont outscored Exeter six tries to none. The win gives
Clermont 10 points from two matches in  Europe ’s elite club
competition. Leinster is second in the pool with eight points
after beating the Scarlets 20-13.  Harlequins beat Connacht 30-22 to lead Pool 3 by four
points over Biarritz, which defeated Zebre 38-17. Saracens top
Pool 1 by five points after routing Racing Metro 30-13, and
Toulouse took the Pool 2 lead with a 33-21 win over Treviso.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  